snippet.title: DCP Web Designers
snippet.description:
Welcome to DCP Web Designers YouTube Channel. If you want to learn new tech skills then our channel is the right place for you. You can find 700+ free video tutorials on a wide range of software apps such as:

GIMP
Photoshop
Blender 3D
Movie Edit Pro
Davinci Resolve
Premiere Pro
Libre Office Cal, Writer, Impress
OpenOffice Cal, Writer, Impress
Microsoft Excel Word, Outlook, Powerpoint
Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, Instagram
YouTube
Google Chrome
HTML5 and CSS3
Woocommerce
WordPress 
Small Business Bookkeeping
Google Chrome 
PayPal

My ultimate goal is to share as much of my knowledge as possible for FREE! Why may ask why am I doing that? Well, someone had to teach me right? So why not share that knowledge and help other people? Lots of my knowledge has been gained from reading many books over the years, but I find video tutorials are easier to understand and follow. So, join me on this knowledge journey and don't forget to have fun!

Pankaj Shah

DCP Web Designers

www.dcpweb.co.uk
